    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Plans illustrating the piles, which are architectural foundation elements comprising timber, steel, or precast concrete columns that serve as subsurface supports for vertical loads.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000001271/AIA, Architect's Handbook of Professional Practice (1970)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Se refiere a planos que ilustran los pilotes, que corresponden a los elementos de cimentación arquitectónica, comprenden columnas de madera, acero u hormigón armado que sirven como soportes de sub-superficies para cargas verticales.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Verwijst naar plattegronden met daarop aangegeven de heipalen: de bouwkundige funderingselementen die bestaan uit kolommen van hout, staal of voorgestort beton welke als ondergrondse ondersteuning van een verticale last fungeren.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052374/Polytechnisch woordenboek En-Ne (1991)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>呈現打樁規劃之製圖，樁柱為木材、鋼鐵或預鑄混凝土柱所組成的建築基礎元素，針對垂直荷重提供地下支撐。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052784/TELDAP database (2009-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Plantas que ilustram pilares, elementos da fundação arquitetônica compostos de madeira, ferro ou colunas de concreto pré-moldado que servem como suportes de subsuperfície para cargas verticais.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Portuguese</Note_Language>
